Unlike `closePairThm21_case1_BmiddlePartExp`, this local exponent restricts
only the cofactor monomial, leaving the selected-minor diagonal contribution
in the common residual. -/
noncomputable def closePairThm21_case1_BmiddleCofactorPartExp
