/-- The coefficient obtained by collecting all raw equality-case terms with
the same `(K,d)` key.  This version deliberately avoids `CollectedIndex`,
because the subtype `{q // q ∈ keyFinset ...}` may be empty and can trigger
unwanted `Nonempty` synthesis. -/
